templates.template_query: What percentage of {department_0} department hours did {employee_0} contribute in {time_period_0}?
templates.sql_template: SELECT (COALESCE(emp.emp_hours, 0) / NULLIF(COALESCE(dept.dept_hours, 0), 0)) * 100 as percentage FROM (SELECT COALESCE(SUM(w.hour), 0) as emp_hours FROM work_hour w JOIN employee e ON w.employee_id = e.uuid WHERE e.department = '{department_0}' AND e.name = '{employee_0}' AND NOT (w.start_date > '{time_period_0}-end' OR w.end_date < '{time_period_0}-start')) as emp, (SELECT COALESCE(SUM(w.hour), 0) as dept_hours FROM work_hour w JOIN employee e ON w.employee_id = e.uuid WHERE e.department = '{department_0}' AND NOT (w.start_date > '{time_period_0}-end' OR w.end_date < '{time_period_0}-start')) as dept
